title: Taxi Complete Series Seasons 1-5
description: This is a collection of the entire 5 season TV series "Taxi" that ran from 1978-1983. This torrent was compiled from several different torrents that purported to be complete. This collection has correct naming for all episodes and all episodes are complete in their content. They are of fairly decent quality, some are DVDRips and some are TVRips but they are all watchable as AVIs. I have personally watched all episodes in their entirety and didn't run into any playback issues using VLC on Windows
